About Us




Nurturing Entrepreneurs through Partnerships


                                     



A front runner since its inception in 1975, the Apollo Group entered its global phase in 1994 as it launched AIL with the dual goals of internationalizing its core business and diversification. AIL has been successful in achieving both.



Management
 
Mr. Raaja Kanwar
Vice Chairman and 
Managing Director, 
Apollo International Limited


 
 
 



Mission

Nurturing and facilitating entrepreneurship to build a truly global enterprise by providing a platform of over three decades of business experience, reputation, corporate strength and environment conducive for growth of all.





Businesses




Businesses
Established in the year 1994, Apollo International Limited (AIL) is a multidimensional organisation with diversified operations across various business areas. AIL's business areas include Integrated Logistics Solutions, Marketing &amp; Distribution of Tyres, Tubes, Flaps and Rims, International Business and Export of Various Products, Equipment & Projects, Manufacturing and Export of Leather Garment and Accessories.

                             





Logistics



Tyre Marketing & Distribution



International Business 



Leather









Group Companies




Group Companies
 
AIL has been established with a vision of ‘Nurturing Entrepreneurs through Partnerships’ and the group companies live up to it in every possible manner.

                             

































Social Commitment

















